title: DoneEx XCell Compiler 1.8.1 NEW.rar
description:
DoneEx XCell Compiler is the unique compiler for MS Excel XLS files which allows you to turn XLS workbook logic into portable EXE application (which require MS Excel to run) with hidden formulas and attach XLA Add-Ins to EXE.

XCell Compiler also allows you to promote your company name and/or trade mark by attaching your own image as splash screen in final EXE package.
